  "body_html": "<p>此门学科研究 <code>随机现象</code> 的 <code>统计规律性</code>。</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><strong>统计规律性</strong>：在大量重复试验中，呈现出的固有规律性。如重复抛硬币。</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><strong>随机现象</strong>：单次试验中结果呈现不确定性，大量重复试验中结果又具有统计规律性的现象。</p><p><br /></p><h3 id=\"NeSPt\">样本空间</h3><p>随机试验的可能结果集合。</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">掷硬币的样本空间为 {正，反}</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">掷骰子的样本空间为 <span>{1,2,3,4,5,6}</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">城市发生交通事故的次数，样本空间为 <span>{0,1,2,3,4,5,6....}</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span><br /></span></p><h3 id=\"ewFoH\">如何计算样本空间？</h3><p>掷硬币，基本事件是 2，抛 3 次，则样本空间 = 2<sup>3</sup> = 2×2×2 = 8；抛 10 次，则<span>样本空间 = 2</span><sup><span>10</span></sup></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><h3 id=\"Fgdv9\">随机事件</h3><p>事件是样本空间的子集，掷骰子有 6 个基本事件：<span>{1},</span><span>{2},</span><span>{3},</span><span>{4},</span><span>{5},</span><span>{6}</span></p><p>事件的关系：</p><p><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2019/png/85998/1558770787603-5b604514-5761-48f5-acaf-0497223ba02c.png#align=left&amp;display=inline&amp;height=105&amp;originHeight=486&amp;originWidth=758&amp;status=done&amp;width=163\" style=\"max-width: 600px; width: 163px;\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/__latex/0829539f10804a325eaceff2c3c43ac1.svg#card=math&amp;code=A%20%5Csubset%20B&amp;height=24&amp;width=49\" style=\"max-width: 600px; width: 49px;\" /><img alt=\"image.png\" title=\"image.png\" src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2019/png/85998/1558770817821-1142a7d7-22d8-4290-964b-96df0632a908.png#align=left&amp;display=inline&amp;height=103&amp;name=image.png&amp;originHeight=474&amp;originWidth=726&amp;size=152663&amp;status=done&amp;width=158\" style=\"max-width: 600px; width: 158px;\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/__latex/b910c111ac8440bf4f4863bb5fc83aa8.svg#card=math&amp;code=A%20%5Ccup%20B&amp;height=24&amp;width=45\" style=\"max-width: 600px; width: 45px;\" /><img alt=\"image.png\" title=\"image.png\" src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2019/png/85998/1558770858607-27ed487d-bdf6-4390-9ebb-5c604865a694.png#align=left&amp;display=inline&amp;height=104&amp;name=image.png&amp;originHeight=266&amp;originWidth=408&amp;size=34411&amp;status=done&amp;width=160\" style=\"max-width: 600px; width: 160px;\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/__latex/b86fc6b051f63d73de262d4c34e3a0a9.svg#card=math&amp;code=AB&amp;height=24&amp;width=26\" style=\"max-width: 600px; width: 26px;\" /><span> 或 <img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/__latex/36644e97756f76b26077c7c828edc492.svg#card=math&amp;code=A%20%5Ccap%20B&amp;height=24&amp;width=45\" style=\"max-width: 600px; width: 45px;\" /></span></p><p><img alt=\"image.png\" title=\"image.png\" src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2019/png/85998/1558770868608-e39afd8c-2a27-41f4-a24c-95d1e0f4e638.png#align=left&amp;display=inline&amp;height=103&amp;name=image.png&amp;originHeight=262&amp;originWidth=408&amp;size=40663&amp;status=done&amp;width=161\" style=\"max-width: 600px; width: 161px;\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/__latex/3d3c0bb422b55003c65dc2e7d55e4e82.svg#card=math&amp;code=A%20-%20B&amp;height=24&amp;width=47\" style=\"max-width: 600px; width: 47px;\" /><span> </span><img alt=\"image.png\" title=\"image.png\" src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2019/png/85998/1558770886884-7058c697-0ccc-4617-a7f0-7b82242b62bd.png#align=left&amp;display=inline&amp;height=106&amp;name=image.png&amp;originHeight=262&amp;originWidth=392&amp;size=88576&amp;status=done&amp;width=158\" style=\"max-width: 600px; width: 158px;\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/__latex/4e910df906403d34de268a5ca1b810e9.svg#card=math&amp;code=%5Coverline%7BA%7D%3D1-A&amp;height=27&amp;width=79\" style=\"max-width: 600px; width: 79px;\" /><span> 逆事件</span></p><p><img alt=\"image.png\" title=\"image.png\" src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2019/png/85998/1558770876953-1df1d1f6-9e8c-4715-a5ae-c915f5d7c5d7.png#align=left&amp;display=inline&amp;height=103&amp;name=image.png&amp;originHeight=258&amp;originWidth=398&amp;size=18710&amp;status=done&amp;width=159\" style=\"max-width: 600px; width: 159px;\" /> <img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/__latex/1074e73e7e05c3fd6a51cbc0aedd8163.svg#card=math&amp;code=AB%3D%5Cvarnothing&amp;height=24&amp;width=62\" style=\"max-width: 600px; width: 62px;\" /><span> A 与 B 不相容或互斥</span></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>交换律<span>：</span><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/__latex/bc2a0f9ac63d73602d5f731ab5e2cf74.svg#card=math&amp;code=A%20%5Ccup%20B%3DB%20%5Ccup%20A%2C%20A%20B%3DB%20A&amp;height=24&amp;width=194\" style=\"max-width: 600px; width: 194px;\" /></p><p>结合律<span>：</span><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/__latex/6221e02683eaa8929754dabb93e345c0.svg#card=math&amp;code=A%20%5Ccup%28B%20%5Ccup%20C%29%3D%28A%20%5Ccup%20B%29%20%5Ccup%20C%2C%20A%28B%20C%29%3D%28A%20B%29%20C&amp;height=24&amp;width=337\" style=\"max-width: 600px; width: 337px;\" /></p><p>分配率<span>：</span><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/__latex/c8662cadb32669a5612e6f383895aaa4.svg#card=math&amp;code=A%28B%20%5Ccup%20C%29%3D%28A%20B%29%20%5Ccup%28A%20C%29%2C%20A%20%5Ccup%28B%20C%29%3D%28A%20%5Ccup%20B%29%28A%20%5Ccup%20C%29&amp;height=24&amp;width=408\" style=\"max-width: 600px; width: 408px;\" /></p><p>对偶律(De Morgan 律)<span>：</span><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/__latex/cdd8651dc036882a99d606ffdd59a901.svg#card=math&amp;code=%5Coverline%7BA%20%5Ccup%20B%7D%3D%5Coverline%7BA%7D%20%5Coverline%7BB%7D%2C%20%5Coverline%7BA%20B%7D%3D%5Coverline%7BA%7D%20%5Ccup%20%5Coverline%7BB%7D&amp;height=27&amp;width=199\" style=\"max-width: 600px; width: 199px;\" /></p><p>对于多个随机事件, 上述运算律也成立。</p><p><br /></p><p>此外还有</p><p>吸收率：<img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/__latex/bf71aa4729f3c713a128b4afffa664b6.svg#card=math&amp;code=A%20%5Ccup%20%5COmega%3D%5COmega%2C%20A%20%5COmega%3DA%2C%20A%20%5Ccup%20%5Cvarnothing%3DA%2C%20A%20%5Ccap%20%5Cvarnothing%3D%5Cvarnothing&amp;height=24&amp;width=325\" style=\"max-width: 600px; width: 325px;\" /></p><p>重余律：<img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/__latex/870f916ea48e424f08fd176df319be53.svg#card=math&amp;code=%5Coverline%7B%5Coverline%7BA%7D%7D%3DA&amp;height=33&amp;width=50\" style=\"max-width: 600px; width: 50px;\" /></p><p>幂等律：<img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/__latex/104b351b49ca6144084773a829f46bbd.svg#card=math&amp;code=A%20%5Ccup%20A%3DA%2C%20A%20%5Ccap%20A%3DA&amp;height=24&amp;width=168\" style=\"max-width: 600px; width: 168px;\" /></p><p><span>差化积：</span><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/__latex/1ac462966cf0a5156a340b56c9bb3ffe.svg#card=math&amp;code=A-B%3DA%20%5Coverline%7BB%7D%3DA-A%20B&amp;height=27&amp;width=178\" style=\"max-width: 600px; width: 178px;\" /><span> 不理解的话看看图</span></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><h3 id=\"nKLgM\">常见例子</h3><p>A 和 B 至少有一个发生<span>：</span><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/__latex/b910c111ac8440bf4f4863bb5fc83aa8.svg#card=math&amp;code=A%20%5Ccup%20B&amp;height=24&amp;width=45\" style=\"max-width: 600px; width: 45px;\" /></p><p>A 和 B 同时发生：<img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/__latex/b86fc6b051f63d73de262d4c34e3a0a9.svg#card=math&amp;code=AB&amp;height=24&amp;width=26\" style=\"max-width: 600px; width: 26px;\" /></p><p><br /></p><p><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/__latex/2c494129c2542ff4981630478d1847c6.svg#card=math&amp;code=%5Coverline%7BA%20%20B%7D&amp;height=27&amp;width=27\" style=\"max-width: 600px; width: 27px;\" /><span>  表示 A 和 B 不同时发生</span></p><p><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/__latex/02a9430151bc4cd9d7ad0296884dd6e2.svg#card=math&amp;code=%5Coverline%7BA%7D%5Coverline%7BB%7D&amp;height=27&amp;width=27\" style=\"max-width: 600px; width: 27px;\" /><span>  表示 A 和 B 都不发生，两者是不一样的</span></p><p>两者的联系是 <img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/__latex/b026171ec1209ab2f3ad0bb879f35706.svg#card=math&amp;code=%5Cbegin%7Bequation%7D%0A%5Coverline%7BA%20B%7D%3D%5Coverline%7BA%7D%20%5Coverline%7BB%7D%20%5Ccup%20A%20%5Coverline%7BB%7D%20%5Ccup%20%5Coverline%7BA%7D%20B%0A%5Cend%7Bequation%7D&amp;height=27&amp;width=168\" style=\"max-width: 600px; width: 168px;\" /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><img alt=\"image.png\" title=\"image.png\" src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2019/png/85998/1558786923286-cadcae5f-715b-4b2d-bb76-8f4c6aa91b1f.png#align=left&amp;display=inline&amp;height=276&amp;name=image.png&amp;originHeight=1031&amp;originWidth=1908&amp;size=692788&amp;status=done&amp;width=511\" style=\"max-width: 600px; width: 511px;\" /></p><p><br /></p><p><img alt=\"image.png\" title=\"image.png\" src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2019/png/85998/1558787056392-3e18ffd9-4751-49e5-b08c-ac79c86c5b7c.png#align=left&amp;display=inline&amp;height=225&amp;name=image.png&amp;originHeight=843&amp;originWidth=1901&amp;size=496877&amp;status=done&amp;width=507\" style=\"max-width: 600px; width: 507px;\" /></p><p><br /></p>",
